name: Equitable cancer care and prevention
description: Funding is provided to BreastScreen Victoria (BSV) to deliver additional breast cancer screening across new and existing services. Additional investment is provided to replace radiotherapy linear accelerators in Ballarat and Geelong, and install a new radiotherapy linear accelerator in Traralgon.
